{"tid":1545574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"告密眾籌，有冇得諗","createTime":"2019-09-06T03:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:31:22.000Z","uid":315003,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b62ebd832c35019bd2f8bd4045b870a81b7f79","tid":1545574,"uid":315003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:18:46.000Z","msg":"P牌第一次開post, 希望大家見諒<br />\n<br />\n今日重點在於要攞返8.31太子地鐵入面既CCTV片, 大家可以諗諗可否搞個告密眾籌，仿效689懸紅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地可以訂啲rule例如<br />\n- 要提供既證據要法庭採納先計<br />\n- 保障告密者身份 <br />\n- 幫佢轉做污點證人或豁免檢控權 (利申唔係法律撚)<br />\n<br />\n俗語話 有錢洗得鬼推磨<br />\n<br />\n威逼唔到我地利誘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果籌到HKD 2-3m可以買返個真相，我覺得抵過登報。加上如果證據夠實可以係唔曝露身份下出現， 兩三球比散仔狗，黨鐵職員，或涉事市民工，呢個誘因都吸引呀。<br />\n<br />\n我明最後如果籌左比狗大家會覺得好冇道理，但電視都有線人費，我地可不用一切方法令到公眾知道真相？可能我地用幾球就可以令核彈爆發，中共瓦解？<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 唔識搞眾籌 有冇巴絲可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"af2882c53a251d3d9f33559f628a5405b32b2105","tid":1545574,"uid":34962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"da96af73c9fdc47bdd1c7320616dac2b36d11b7e","tid":1545574,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"907 機場攻略正式出爐，唔使再驚大逃走！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544251</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http